ps://api.zhihu.com/questions/321739372","type":"question","created":1556212839,"answer_count":67,"follower_count":3012,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[767,21767,42364],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"十年书龄了，主要看玄幻类型，基本上出名的都看过了。近几年，看文真的是越来越挑剔。也越来越没有耐心。很多文章看个五六章，吸引不了我的直接PASS，但凡有一点圣母倾向的PASS，小白爽文更不用说了，最近几个月，完完全全是没有书看的一个状态。所以就萌生了自己写一本书的想法。 打算写的时候还充满着幻想，寻思都是人，他们能写，我也能，等到写了两章之后，自己读了一下，连小白爽文都比我写的好看。因为特别喜欢滚开大大的书，所以特地去重新翻了翻滚开大大那几本书，发现我在写故事的时候，就是在干巴巴堆故事，没有一点点代入感，而滚开大大的文章，发现只需几笔，就可以把一个虚构的世界生动形象的描写出来。几局对话，几句描写，整个人物就鲜活了起来。所以很想问问该如何练习这种写作思路。"},"attached_info":"Cj8I07TPz9iultEuEAMaCDMzNzczNzAyIOfYh+YFMAA4xBdAMHIJMzIxNzM5MzcyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-70943805d9a1ff3bcc3aa301b994b652_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"49_1637288665.9538314","card_id":"Q_486968186","target":{"id":486968186,"title":"正确的刷牙方式是什么？电动牙刷值得买吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/486968186","type":"question","created":1631679578,"answer_count":43,"follower_count":183,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[6239,11103,18012],"comment_count":2,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I07TPz9iultEuEAMaCDcwNDk2Nzc1INrohYoGMAI4twFAMXIJNDg2OTY4MTg2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picb.zhimg.com/50/v2-ed026330615a031a7ace8ed49a39f6d9_b.jpg"}]}],"description":{"time":"2021-11-19 10:24:26"}}